#: lib/retro_hex_chat/games/catalog.ex:172
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Top-down boxing — close punches score more. "
msgstr "Бокс сверху вниз — ближние удары забивают больше."

#: lib/retro_hex_chat/games/catalog.ex:408
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Top-down ice hockey in a cyberpunk arena — control your field player, "
